    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The study and practice of caring for and waiting on the sick, injured, or others unable to look after themselves or to deal with their specific medical needs.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
